The '''Security and Intelligence Council''', also known as '''Palpatine's War Council''', or the '''Military Advisory Council''', was a committee of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It consisted of [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Darth Sidious|Palpatine's]] most trusted advisers, though membership changed often. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Jannie Ha'Nook]] was a ranking member, along with [[Vice Chair/Legends|Vice Chair]] [[Mas Amedda/Legends|Mas Amedda]], [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]], [[Armand Isard/Legends|Armand Isard]] and [[Kohl Seerdon]].

